1da783d6cb9bc3721a47146a10f4d92d3b6905e","tid":54940,"uid":61593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T11:01:16.000Z","msg":"開大聲睇片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae70f66003789c10dbfb61f001aa562892a1ab68","tid":54940,"uid":59550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T11:11:00.000Z","msg":"有次一班廢老入車廂就死逼爛逼行到中間位，仲要攞任成個大電飯煲盒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />然後又大大聲聲講野，出車仲過分，直頭推開我男朋友個袋逼出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大佬呀我地都落緊就唔好搶住出喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"864927f28dbd7173173b548390f38f4d72df9c88","tid":54940,"uid":59550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T11:12:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有次一班廢老入車廂就死逼爛逼行到中間位，仲要攞<span style=\"color: red;\">住成個</span>大電飯煲盒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />然後又大大聲聲講野，出車仲過分，直頭推開我男朋友個袋逼出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大佬呀我地都落緊就唔好搶住出喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"ee245cc61674527f0b0dd68f7a83d1e232c0ead9","tid":54940,"uid":4736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T06:16:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有次一班廢老入車廂就死逼爛逼行到中間位，仲要攞任成個大電飯煲盒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />然後又大大聲聲講野，出車仲過分，直頭推開我男朋友個袋逼出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大佬呀我地都落緊就唔好搶住出喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n廢老繁忙時間撘地鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2389624163bf0c40a46bc36f78b4206615d532ef","tid":54940,"uid":4534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T06:23:06.000Z","msg":"岩岩搭地鐵 個呀婆拖住個孫 <br />\n晏晝都其實少人搭<br />\n仲要係頭果幾個站 大把位坐<br />\n我行入車廂先 諗住坐低<br />\n個呀婆驚死無位坐<br />\n勁大聲：嘩無位呀 跟住推開我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n心諗 成排都空既你都要推人<br />\n多到比你訓係道都仲得呀"},{"pid":"0cea82a7f3be25147b9085c4c54f3f69c1d90f6d","tid":54940,"uid":45082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T06:23:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>搶關愛座</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  大部份係搶普通位</blockquote><br />\n呢個最仆街 有關愛座唔坐<br />\n搞到個位吉咗無人敢坐<br />\n話時話 班廢老知唔知<br />\n自己某啲行為係好剋人憎"},{"pid":"11f000bfc89b37ef3c2baf636a50080057ebe9d9","tid":54940,"uid":377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T06:24:37.000Z","msg":"食橙"},{"pid":"1071dbc14d55eddb965ae296109a69f1c7333ea4","tid":54940,"uid":58119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T07:38:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>搶關愛座</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  大部份係搶普通位</blockquote><br />\n呢個最仆街 有關愛座唔坐<br />\n搞到個位吉咗無人敢坐<br />\n話時話 班廢老知唔知<br />\n自己某啲行為係好剋人憎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢地唔撚知 我呀媽差唔多50歲 佢都識話班廢老唔應該繁忙時間出街 佢話佢第時再老啲一定唔會咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}